                    </span>
                    <span class="tag-box invisible">
                        <span class="inline-tag">MIME</span>
                    </span>
                    <span class="sub-box">
                        Enthält den MIME [*]
                        <span class="footnote"><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i> <em>Multipurpose Internet Mail
